               <msContents>
                  <summary>
                     <p>I) ዳዊት, Psalter (fols. <locus from="4r" to="208vb"/>)I-<locus target="#1"/>) መዝሙረ፡ዳዊት“Psalms of  David” (fols. <locus from="4r" to="166r"/>) I-<locus target="#2"/>) መኃልየ፡ነቢያት“The Canticles of the Prophets” (fols. <locus from="166r" to="182v"/>) I-<locus target="#3"/>) መኃልየ፡መኃልይ፡ዘሰሎሞን“Song of Songs of Solomon” (fols. <locus from="182v" to="191v"/>) I-<locus target="#4"/>) ውዳሴ፡ማርያም“The Praise of Mary” (fols. <locus from="192ra" to="204ra"/>) </p>
                     <p>I-<locus target="#5"/>) አንቀጸ፡ብርሃን“Gate of Light”(fols. <locus from="204ra" to="208vb"/>), incomplete, the end is missing</p>
                     
                     
                     
                  </summary>
              
               </msContents>
